Key Match Events: Jack Kochanowicz pitched seven strong innings in a walk-off 4-3 win in 13 innings over the White Sox.
Jordyn Adams hit a game-winning RBI infield single for his first career walk-off hit.
Post-Match Reflections: Jordyn Adams credited his teammates, especially Kochanowicz, for putting him in the position to achieve the walk-off hit.
Jack Kochanowicz expressed confidence in his recent performance and aims to continue his success into the next season.
